Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: No school prayers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcnd
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Mar 1984
Senate fails to support suggested constitutional amendment which would have ushered in school prayers across the US. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less